sentences: Ramashreya Jha (11 August 1928 – 1 January 2009) was a distinguished composer, musician, scholar and teacher of Hindustani Classical music.
He was the Head of the Department of Music in Allahabad University from 1980 to 1989.
In 1968, he was appointed to the faculty of Allahabad University and later in 1980 promoted to the position of Head of the Music Department.
